column2: SELECT top #   gal.specObjID as ID_gal,   gal.lgm_tot_p5# as mass_tot_gal,   gal.lgm_fib_p5# as mass_fib_gal,   gal.sfr_tot_p5# as ssfr_tot_gal,   gal.sfr_fib_p5# as ssfr_fib_gal,   ED.specObjID as ID_ED,   ED.logMass_median as mass_ED,   ED.dust1_mean as dust1_ED,   ED.dust2_mean as dust2_ED,   ED.age_mean as age_ED,   ED.ssfr_mean and ssfr_ED,   ENoD.specObjID as ID_ENoD,   ENoD.logMass_median as mass_ENoD,   ENoD.dust1_mean as dust1_ENoD,   ENoD.dust2_mean as dust2_ENoD,   ENoD.age_mean as age_ENoD,   ENoD.ssfr_mean as ssfr_ENoD,   WD.specObjID as ID_WD,   WD.logMass_median as mass_WD,   WD.dust1_mean as dust1_WD,   WD.dust2_mean as dust2_WD,   WD.age_mean as age_WD,   WD.ssfr_mean as ssfr_WD,   WNoD.specObjID as ID_WNoD,   WNoD.logMass_median as mass_WNoD,   WNoD.dust1_mean as dust1_WNoD,   WNoD.dust2_mean as dust2_WNoD,   WNoD.age_mean as age_WNoD,   WNoD.ssfr_mean as ssfr_WNoD    FROM galSpecExtra gal   JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust ED ON ED.specObjID = gal.specObjID   JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust ENoD ON ENoD.specObjID = gal.specObjID   JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust WD ON WD.specObjID = gal.specObjID   JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideNoDust WNoD ON WNoD.specObjID = gal.specObjID
